<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5702795">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5702795/" class="title-link">《大连接》：社会网络不仅是“网络”，更是“社会”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5702795"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/riali/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2157561-25.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/riali/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">白小茉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-17"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-17 23:17:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5702795_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  刊登于《新商务周刊》2012年第10期  近几年，现代社会中“网络科学”的独特魅力越来越引起人们的注意。对于“网络科学”的概念稍加厘清，就不难发现“网络科学”不仅仅体现在互联网及全球通信的快速成长上，人体神经元之间的通信、疾病在世界范围内的爆发轨迹，乃至新闻与信息...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5702795_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5702795_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



